<C>__{operator}
<D>__{you're sure?}
<A>__{changeling a true story}
<C>__{christine}
<D>__{positive. go on, have fun.}
<A>__{they head off. christine focuses on her work. there's another knock on the door.}
<C>__{christine}
<D>__{i said i can't go }
